# Naming, Folders, and Styling

- Folder names describe the topic. The **index file holds the code**.
    - e.g. `components > features > biometric > index.tsx`
    - e.g. `hooks > useMediaQuery > index.ts`
    - e.g. `lib > utils > date > index.ts`
- Screens use paired CSS Modules:
    - `screens > ContactUs > index.tsx`
    - `screens > ContactUs > index.module.scss`
    - Inside component: `import styles from './index.module.scss'`
    - Apply Tailwind utility semantics **as class names inside SCSS modules**:
        - `.root { @apply container mx-auto p-4; }`
        - `.disclaimer { @apply text-xs text-muted-foreground; }`
